Scale_GetTitle
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Scale=>scale/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Scale_GetTitle
Veneer:	<scale_get_title>
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = Scale object ID
r2 = 6
r3 = pointer to buffer
r4 = size of buffer
{f}
#indent

On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r4 = size of buffer required (if r3=0)
     else buffer contains title text.
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the title for the Scale object.